        <div1 type="body">
            

<p>To Colonel Austin.</p>

<p>Respected Sir, Tho I am only acquainted with you by 
reputation I take the liberty of addressing you a few lines desiring you
to be so good as to write me concerning the situation of the <placeName>colony</placeName>
you are forming on the <placeName>Brazos </placeName>I passed thro' that <placeName>country </placeName>about
<date n="xx-xx-1824">thre years ago</date> with <persName>Gen. Bernardo's family</persName> and think it a fine 
country of land. I wish you to inform me of the conditions imposed upon
the <persName>settlers   </persName>Write to <persName>Pablo Willis J. Powell</persName> Naturalista in <placeName>Mexico</placeName>.</p>

<p><persName>Willis J. Powell </persName>   [Rubric]</p>

<p><placeName>Mexico </placeName>the <date when="1827-06-24">24th. of June 1827</date>.</p>

<p>[Addressed:] Al <persName>Señor Coronel Austin</persName> en el <placeName>Rio de los Brazos</placeName> en
la <placeName>Provincia de Texas</placeName>&#8212;. pr. el <placeName>camino del Saltillo en Coahuila</placeName></p>


        </div1>
